Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:18.91,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}雷鳴を感じる心は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.00,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}響かせよう 心から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:29.13,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}そう彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:35.99,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}小さい光　Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:19.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}遠古之光 Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:34.31,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}霧之夜 被那黑暗所困
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:45.91,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}只有氣息存在著周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:54.63,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}那幻之花瓣
